Class PriceStatus

java.lang.Object
com.tectonica.jonix.onix2.PriceStatus
All Implemented Interfaces:
OnixElement<PriceStatuss>, OnixTag, Serializable
public class PriceStatus extends Object implements OnixElement<PriceStatuss>, Serializable

Price status

An ONIX code which specifies the status of a price. Optional and non-repeating. If the field is omitted, the default “unspecified” will apply.

Format Fixed-length, two numeric digits
Codelist List 61
Reference name <PriceStatus>
Short tag <j266>
Example <PriceStatus>01</PriceStatus> Provisional

This tag may be included in the following composites:

  • <Price>
Possible placements within ONIX message:
  • Product ⯈ SupplyDetail ⯈ Price ⯈ PriceStatus
  • Product ⯈ SupplyDetail ⯈ Reissue ⯈ Price ⯈ PriceStatus
